      "post": {
        "summary": "Add users (existing users) or emails (new users) to a seat in subscription",
        "operationId": "addSeatUsersToSubscription",
        "description": "Add one or more users to a seat in subscription. User can only have one subscription per service (as seat user or as owner), the amount of available seats is defined in seat_quota of subscription. One or more emails can also be sent for users that do not yet exist in Netilion, the users emails will then be invited to join Netilion. ```Either id or email pro entry should be provided (not both).``` If an email is provided for existing user, then given user will be used.",
