        "description": "**Deprecated**: This endpoint is deprecated and will be removed in a future. Please check V2 of the Netilion API for the new endpoints.\n\nCreate or update display labels for an instrumentation in your accessible\nscope. To add display labels, just add key (instrumentation value key) and set\nthe value with needed string. Keys for display labels are unique per instrumentation\nand can only be added once. Keys can only consist of [a-z A-Z 0-9 . - _ ]. For\na key that is send multiple times in the request body, only the last key-value\nis saved.",
